<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Toyota Fortuner | AutoNexus</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/images/favicon.png" />
    <!-- Bootstrap 5 CDN -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style.css">
<%- include('partials/car-style') %>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Navbar (logo width 200, height 50, border-radius 10px) -->
<%- include('partials/navbar') %>

    <!-- Car Details Section -->
    <div class="car-details-container">
        <h1 class="car-title">Toyota Fortuner <span style="font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400;">(Rs 25.71 - 31.48 Lakh*)</span></h1>
        
        <!-- Car Image Viewer -->
        <div class="image-viewer-container">
            <button class="image-viewer-btn left" onclick="prevImage()" aria-label="Previous Image">&#8592;</button>
            <img src="/images/f-1.jpg" class="image-viewer-img" id="carImage" alt="Toyota Fortuner">
            <button class="image-viewer-btn right" onclick="nextImage()" aria-label="Next Image">&#8594;</button>
        </div>

        <!-- Car Description -->
        <div class="car-description">
            <p>
                The Toyota Fortuner is a robust and stylish SUV, offering a blend of power, comfort, and advanced features. With its impressive road presence and reliable performance, the Fortuner is a favorite among SUV enthusiasts in India. The Fortuner is offered in six variants, encompassing two engine options, two transmissions and two drive types. The petrol Fortuner is a 4x2 only, with the 2.7-litre engine being paired with a 5-speed manual or an optional 6-speed automatic. Diesel duties are being carried out by the 2.8-litre motor. This engine gets a choice of a 6-speed manual or a 6-speed automatic, and is made available with four-wheel drive as well.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Car Info Tables -->
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-6 d-flex">
                <div class="info-box flex-fill mx-2 ">
                    <div class="section-heading">Economy & Performance</div>
                    <table  class="car-info-table">
                        <thead>
                            <tr>
                                <th>Economy</th>
                                <th>Performance</th>
                            </tr>
                        </thead>
                        <tbody>
                            <tr>
                                <td>Mileage: 15.04 kmpl</td>
                                <td>Engine: 2755 cc</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td>Fuel Type: Diesel</td>
                                <td>BHP: 174.5</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td>Service Cost: Rs 30,875/yr</td>
                                <td>No. of cylinders: 4</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td>Fuel Tank: 80L</td>
                                <td>No. of Gears: 6 Speed</td>
                            </tr>
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 d-flex">
                <div class="info-box flex-fill mx-2">
                    <div class="section-heading">Comfort & Safety</div>
                    <!-- <div style="height: 200px;"></div> -->
                    <table class="car-info-table">
                        <thead>
                            <tr>
                                <th>Comfort</th>
                                <th>Safety</th>
                            </tr>
                        </thead>
                        <tbody>
                            <tr>
                                <td>Transmission: Manual/Automatic</td>
                                <td>ABS: Yes</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td>Rear AC vents: Yes</td>
                                <td>Driver Airbag: Yes</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td>Seating capacity: 7</td>
                                <td>Parking Sensor: Yes</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td>Bootspace: 454L</td>
                                <td>Air Bag: Yes</td>
                            </tr>
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Highlights -->
        <div class="section-heading">Fortuner Highlights</div>
        <div class="car-description">
            <ul>
                <li>
                    Toyota has confirmed the waiting period for the Fortuner currently ranges between 6-10 weeks, even with its production plant working at 95 per cent of its capacity.
                </li>
                <li>
                    The Fortuner is offered in six variants, encompassing two engine options, two transmissions and two drive types.
                </li>
                <li>
                    The petrol Fortuner is a 4x2 only, with the 2.7-litre engine being paired with a 5-speed manual or an optional 6-speed automatic.
                </li>
                <li>
                    Diesel duties are being carried out by the 2.8-litre motor. This engine gets a choice of a 6-speed manual or a 6-speed automatic, and is made available with four-wheel drive as well.
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Book Button Centered -->
        <div class="text-center">
            <a href="/booking" class="book-btn">Book Your Car</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer (background color same as index.ejs) -->
<%- include('partials/footer') %>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script>
        // Image viewer logic
        const images = [
            "/images/f-1.jpg",
            "/images/f-2.jpg",
            "/images/f-3.jpg",
            "/images/f-4.jpg"
        ];
        let currentImg = 0;
        const carImage = document.getElementById('carImage');
        function showImage(idx) {
            currentImg = (idx + images.length) % images.length;
            carImage.src = images[currentImg];
        }
        function prevImage() {
            showImage(currentImg - 1);
        }
        function nextImage() {
            showImage(currentImg + 1);
        }
        // Initialize
        showImage(0);
    </script>